crude (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Unified command-line clients for ATDW, Skal, and Rezdy
    under a crude-<site> <resource> <verb> grammar.
  * Installs three binaries: crude-atdw (ATDW tourism listings), crude-skal
    (Skal Australia member portal), and crude-rezdy (Rezdy products,
    availability, and bookings).

